Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.64,0:00:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In the previous episode, we talked about
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Lion Jay taught Sparky many power-forward techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Their friendship deepens
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.68,0:00:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparky realized that Lion Jay didn’t want to be an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.80,0:00:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Encourage Lion Jay to be brave and be himself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But Lion Jay was forced by his manager’s gratitude for his talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.20,0:00:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They still gave in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.96,0:00:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We have such a large audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.72,0:00:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We must have won a few games.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.72,0:00:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So everyone started paying attention to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this fan want an autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.32,0:01:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So you’re all fans of Team Lion Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.76,0:01:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t believe you don’t even have a single fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.56,0:01:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we’ll reluctantly pretend to be your fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.32,0:01:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s not do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.96,0:01:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Lion Jay is about to enter the arena to prepare for the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go to the audience seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.96,0:01:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s look forward to Lion Jay’s performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.60,0:01:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck in this game!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.96,0:01:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The same to you /
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.96,0:01:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,See you on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.20,0:01:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would Lion Jay greet you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:02:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen, the competition is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The stands were absolutely packed today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.24,0:02:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Team Defenders were the first to take the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.68,0:02:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Go Team Defenders!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up is the one everyone’s been waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Team Lion Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Lion Jay, the ultimate cool guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.76,0:02:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Lion Jay (Lion Jay) is a cool guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Lion Jay, the ultimate cool guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Lion Jay, my favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Lion Jay
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Lion Jay
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lion Jay…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.48,0:02:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Team Lion Heart’s fans are more enthusiastic than we imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.80,0:02:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Lion Jay, the ultimate cool guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.16,0:02:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Lion Jay, my favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Team Lion Heart is now acting like they have home-court advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Home advantage
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,With the cheers of the fans in the audience
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:03:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They played with the same ease as if they were playing on their own training ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, fans also sometimes do things that disrupt our team’s morale.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The match is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire venue was filled with cheers for Team Lion Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.84,0:03:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Team Lion Heart will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The game began, and Team Lion Heart gained possession of the ball first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can stop me all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Team Lion Heart, keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The opportunity has arrived
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My body won’t obey me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I was definitely influenced by the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shi Laina easily defeated Tibbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, just like that, drive and lay up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shi Laina’s dribbling breakthrough suggests the ball is almost certainly in the net.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:04:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly pass the ball to Lion Jay for a stylish alley-oop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Two to zero, that was so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Team Lion Heart scored the first goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.16,0:04:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I lost focus while defending.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s okay, we can get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparky
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Defense
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch me score this goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump - Can’t jump
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The hot pot Lion Jay treated Sparky to was so fragrant and spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the fierce attack of Team Lion Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Team Defenders were completely overwhelmed and unable to fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Team Defenders were completely overwhelmed and unable to fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The score has quickly reached 10-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The children underperformed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Blazey, hurry up and call a halt, think of a solution!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Blazey, say something, Blazey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they can only rely on themselves to overcome the influence of the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Play to the expected level
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s how we’ll have a chance to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do these goats even know how to play ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s practically adults bullying children!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to find an opportunity to score.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t even think about succeeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparky drew a foul from Lion Jay and was awarded free throws.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:06:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Will he be able to score the team’s first goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn’t matter if you commit a foul, as long as you look cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, Sparky! Our chance to score has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This can’t possibly be a fake fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Diving
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn’t fake a fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch me score the first point of the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Not entering
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hugh
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Referee, I want to file a complaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They are interfering with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The referee indicated that the complaint was invalid and the game continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s okay, we still have one ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I must score this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Not entering
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Unexpectedly, Team Lion Heart called a timeout.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Interrupted his fast break
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you call a timeout when you had such a good scoring opportunity?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hair was messed up, you need to redo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we had launched a quick attack just now, that ball would have been a sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You are an idol
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:08:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Every goal must showcase your most handsome moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a big deal as having messy hair
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn’t be good if the fans found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Children, don’t be nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, let Blazey explain the tactics to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Facing the psychological pressure exerted by the audience
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ll have to overcome this on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The game continues
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,easy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, look at the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Lion Jay is so handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.72,0:08:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We can’t let the point difference widen any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Go Lion Jay! Go Lion Jay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can’t stop him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.60,0:09:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He became so timid and hesitant after just a few words from someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nothing like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,let me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,OMG
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Lion Jay got blocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done! You truly deserve to be my disciple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,foul
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He knocked Lion Jay to the ground, but that wasn’t a foul.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that was a foul.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn’t even a foul anymore! A foul! A foul!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s already 10-0, what’s the point of continuing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:09:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back, go back quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,S
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the ones
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don’t like it, go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly launch a counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly return to defense
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We should all enjoy the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus on the game
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do our best in everything we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Such are us
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,strongest
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s right
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We were already being questioned by everyone, weren’t we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,ridiculed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Limiting our space
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But they’ve still managed to keep playing until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest is up to you, Sparky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,bring it on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Lion Jay
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This kid’s pretty good at backfights.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep him away
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Lion Jay
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.56,0:11:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m going to use this ball
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let everyone open their eyes wide and see clearly
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Our basketball
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Team Defenders scored!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.08,0:12:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The real competition has only just begun.
